node.text:
Together with @dovemencare and @thenbpa, we’re changing the narrative about Black boys and men and calling on fans to #CommitToCARENow by taking the pledge to do more.

As the proud son of a teacher, the power of education was instilled in me from a young age. Knowing that opportunities make a difference and that people who look like me are often denied access to them, motivated me to start my foundation, @spida.cares45 

Join me by taking the pledge at CommitToCAREnow.com. #SpidaCares #DoveMenCare #NBPA #CommitToCARENow

node.text:
2020 has been an unpredictable year. My mom and I, in partnership with @adidashoops and @Crayola, would like to
honor the educators who have stepped up to continue teaching despite incredible obstacles. For #WorldTeachersDay, we are sending tools for virtual learning and adidas x Crayola #DONISSUE2 shoes to 20 teachers that have inspired us. Thank you for all you do! #createdwithadidas
